{"tid":1682222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"試著說：「調查警暴專員會」不要說：「獨立調查委員會」","createTime":"2019-10-30T02:18:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T08:03:06.000Z","uid":336524,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c28e8153bba8a72e5560a3ac20ff93d93501bce6","tid":1682222,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:18:47.000Z","msg":"其實我地想要獨立調查委員會都係想佢可以查班差佬同懲罰佢地，咁點解唔叫做調查警暴專員會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成立調查警暴專員會之前，首先要講清楚警暴唔單指黑警暴力行為，包括佢地所有違法行為、暴行。<br />\n<br />\n調查警暴專員會嘅組成必須要有立法會議員（本人提名鄺神、毛姨姨）、律師在內。不接受由政府自己人查自己人。<br />\n<br />\n改名嘅好處：<br />\n加強震懾力，令香港警察更有成為condom嘅感覺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋亦代表我地對黑警嘅不滿升級，如同我地將「香港人加油」變成香港人反抗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1631dbe935d10084cc7bf3ec77c5478805ca82df","tid":1682222,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:19:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a211efdc0dfbf49171c0318e9515cbce1a62378","tid":1682222,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:19:37.000Z","msg":"我係p牌 推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4053c23751543264573eadcd009544c0e0bd5fd","tid":1682222,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:25:05.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"f24237a2a215ed68fe14e243f417643c2c6131d5","tid":1682222,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:25:15.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"9edf64f44a46ab1a916e7d7143b6b5af3e3e8d2a","tid":1682222,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:25:25.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"5c58b1ed6c3f3a4f2e02c0974ac6a2f9a